query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(ct mc) NoMergeJoin(ct mc t mi) NoMergeJoin(ct mc mi t it) */ select min(t.title) AS typical_european_movie
from company_type AS ct
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on ct.id = mc.company_type_id AND ct.kind = 'production companies' AND mc.note like '%(theatrical)%' AND mc.note like '%(France)%'
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mc.movie_id
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info IN ('Swedish',
'Bulgaria',
'America',
'Norwegian',
'German',
'Danish',
'USA',
'English')
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id;
